casebody.data:
Cowle, Appellant, v. Doctor, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. December 19, 1889.) Appeal from first district court.

Argued before Van Hoesen, P. J., and Bookstavee, J.

McEwan & McEwan, for appellant. Hess & Townsend, for respondent.

No opinion. Ordered that the judgment be affirmed, with costs.
